title: Yootheme - Capture premium template (J2.5, J3.x)
description:
Yoo Capture comes with a clean widescreen design, which is topped by a bright two color scheme. Its versatileness makes it perfect for any kind of web site creation, from business websites to photo blogs.

This theme comes with a whole bunch of features. Capture the attention of your visitors with big parallax backgrounds, slants, which you can add to different module positions and an opening sequence animation that will give your website a unique look and feel. On top that you get a modern Widgetkit Bonus Style for the Slideset.

Built on Warp7 and UIkit Capture provides full support for LESS. You can easily create your very own style with just a few clicks in the Customizer and change colors, spacing and fonts without having to write a single line of code. To get you started, Capture already provides 8 different style variations to choose from.
